flowgate (1.1.3-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Fix DoH/DoT: Use HTTPS proxy_pass for port 8443 services.
  * Auto-configure http block with resolver and variables_hash_bucket_size.
  * Security: Add DNS user (blocky/adguardhome) to proxy group for cert access.
  * Security: Auto-detect proxy group (angie, www-data, nginx).
  * Security: Set proper permissions (750/640) on certificate files.
  * Support both Angie (native ACME) and Nginx (certbot) certificate paths.

 -- crims0n <crims0n@minios.dev>  Sun, 11 Jan 2026 20:30:00 +0300

flowgate (1.1.2-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Smart Sync: Try to start services if they are inactive instead of reloading.
  * Sync Check: Warn user if services failed to start after sync.
  * Improve reliability when deploying on fresh servers.

 -- crims0n <crims0n@minios.dev>  Sat, 10 Jan 2026 23:15:03 +0300

flowgate (1.1.1-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Fix Angie stream block auto-enablement during init.
  * Auto-uncomment stream block in default Angie config.
  * Remove default example.conf from /etc/angie/stream.d/.
  * Update README: remove non-existent angie-module-stream package.
  * Stream module is built-in to Angie, no separate package needed.

 -- crims0n <crims0n@minios.dev>  Wed, 08 Jan 2026 18:15:00 +0300

flowgate (1.1.0-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Expand OS detection to support 30+ Linux distributions.
  * Add OS family mapping (debian, rhel, arch, alpine, suse, gentoo, void,
    freebsd).
  * Show install commands only for missing packages in doctor output.
  * Add universal init system support (systemd, openrc, sysvinit, runit, s6).
  * Auto-detect nginx user (www-data, nginx, http, wwwrun) for config files.
  * Rename FlowWeb to Flowgate Web consistently.
  * Fix Makefile install-web target for file installation.
  * Update .gitignore to exclude Debian build artifacts.
  * Add nginx stream module check in doctor command.
  * Add libnginx-mod-stream as dependency for nginx installations.
  * Fix doctor to not require certbot when angie is installed.
  * Improve init command output with clear step descriptions.
  * Auto-run sync after init to apply base configuration.
  * Auto-disable default nginx site during sync to avoid conflicts.
  * Fix ACME challenge routing with default_server directive.

 -- crims0n <crims0n@minios.dev>  Tue, 06 Jan 2026 23:15:06 +0300

